I was surprised at how intolerant the user-agent field is.
In the end I simply replaced the info-url bit:
os-heritrix/0.11.0 (+http://wap100.bl.uk)
having extra info (the [misc]) seemed to cause it to get rejected 
too. So yes nicer errors and perhaps a little more tolerant. 

mark

